    public static enum OptionalHeader.MagicNumber
extends java.lang.Enum<OptionalHeader.MagicNumber>
    The magic number of the PE file, indicating whether it is a PE32, PE32+ or ROM file

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      PE32
      A PE that supports only 32-bit addresses
      PE32_PLUS
      A PE that supports up to 64-bit addresses
      ROM
      A ROM file.
      UNKNOWN
      Magic number could not be read for any reason.
